      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "text": "Overview",
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "RealityKit provides controls that enable interactions specific to each platform and context."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For example, you can allow someone to interact with an entity that already has a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/CollisionComponent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "by adding the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/InputTargetComponent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " component."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "A RealityKit entity can visibly change when someone looks directly at it"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "with a "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/HoverEffectComponent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " component."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Additionally, you can manage an entity’s accessibility information with "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/AccessibilityComponent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
